{"word":"βακτηρία","slug":"βακτηρία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>βακτηρία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>= <a href='S:βάκτρον'><el>βάκτρον</el></a>,\n<p/><i>a staff, cane</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: borne as a badge of office by the <el>δικασταί</el>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/>"}]}